Title = {ASSESSING THE EFFECTIVENESS OF LAND RESTORATION INTERVENTIONS IN DRY LANDS BY MULTITEMPORAL REMOTE SENSING - A CASE STUDY IN OULED DLIM (MARRAKECH, MOROCCO)},
